《'''笨贼一箩筐'''》，是台湾漫画家[[蕭言中|蕭言中]]画的漫画，也是[[台海两岸|台海两岸]]合作的第一部漫画改编3D电影。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2004-07-09/1107438578.html|title=箫言中新作《笨贼一箩筐》将改拍成3D动画电影|language=zh-cn|publisher=新浪|author=|date=2004-07-09|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109205052/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2004-07-09/1107438578.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>为系列单幅漫画，漫画里笨贼常以低级的失误致读者捧腹。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2006-07-11/11061153593.html|title=萧言中参加动画片高峰论坛 画漫画大多是闷骚型|language=zh-cn|publisher=新浪|author=赵唯辰|date=2006-07-11|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109204854/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2006-07-11/11061153593.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>已画四百余单格漫画，现由[[现代出版社|现代出版社]]出版。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2006-07/09/content_59176.htm|title=萧言中驳斥制造弱智漫画说|language=zh-cn|publisher=京华网|author=|date=2006-07-09|accessdate=2015-02-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227084717/http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2006-07/09/content_59176.htm|archivedate=2015-02-27}}</ref>

在多年前，蕭言中在电视看到两个头套丝袜的强盗被逮，就来了灵感画几张，这就是《笨贼一箩筐》的雏形<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://beijingww.qianlong.com/1470/2010/09/13/291@128746.htm|title=萧言中把漫画看作艺术品|language=zh-cn|publisher=北京文网|author=|date=2010-09-13|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227062722/http://beijingww.qianlong.com/1470/2010/09/13/291@128746.htm|archive-date=2015-02-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2010年8月29日刚好满1000幅<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2010-08-29/103918036171s.shtml|title=小学成绩很差 成了漫画大家！|language=zh-cn|publisher=新浪网|author=夏洪玲、李轶天|date=2010-08-29|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2019-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190110013747/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2010-08-29/103918036171s.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

漫画主人公是一高一矮两个头戴丝袜的“笨贼”搭档。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.huaxia.com/zhwh/whxx/2010/08/2059136.html|title=台湾漫画界四大才子之一萧言中画了千幅“笨贼”|language=zh-cn|publisher=华夏经纬网|author=|date=2010-08-27|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924042156/http://www.huaxia.com/zhwh/whxx/2010/08/2059136.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>于5月21日在北京首演。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/cul/2014/06-22/6306862.shtml|title=《笨贼一箩筐》推出升级版 戏剧冲突巧妙(图)|language=zh-cn|publisher=中国新闻网|author=上官云|date=2014-06-22|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305081045/http://www.chinanews.com/cul/2014/06-22/6306862.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/cul/2014/05-14/6171058.shtml|title=黑色犯罪喜剧"笨贼一箩筐"将首演 原著萧言中(图)|language=zh-cn|publisher=中国新闻网|author=|date=2014-05-14|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305082330/http://www.chinanews.com/cul/2014/05-14/6171058.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

